#. type: Plain text
#: documentation/content/en/books/handbook/wine/_index.adoc:692
#, fuzzy
msgid ""
"Next, set permissions for this new directory to allow only desired users to "
"access it. One approach to this is to create a new group such as "
"\"windows,\" add the desired users to that group (see the sub-section on "
"groups in the crossref:basics[users-groups,Users and Basic Account "
